{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e987fbb238","title":"给张明霞的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3472ad1f57","index":0,"year":1957,"month":11,"day":25,"articleId":"e987fbb238"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"9cc360d5fe","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张明霞，当时在湖南师范学院语文系读书。"},{"id":"c094705019","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"即《蝶恋花·答李淑一》一词。这首词是毛泽东1957年5月11日写给当时的湖南长沙第十中学语文教员李淑一的，原题为《蝶恋花·游仙》。在给张明霞的这封信中，毛泽东改《游仙》为《赠季淑一》。1963年人民文学出版社出版的《毛泽东诗词》中，这首词的题目改为《蝶恋花·答季淑一》。"},{"id":"017a9aa746","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指《鹰之歌》。这是湖南师范学院语文系张明霞等9位同学组织的“十月诗社”办的一个油印诗刊。他们从长沙市第十中学季淑一处抄录毛泽东写的《蝶恋花》词以后，于1957年6月1日写信给毛泽东，要求允许在《鹰之歌》上发表。毛泽东回信时《鹰之歌》已停刊，这首词于1958年1月1日在湖南师范学院院刊《湖南师院》首次发表，题为《蝶恋花·赠季淑一》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bfbab308ac","type":"title","text":"给张明霞的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238"},{"id":"9cc360d5fe","type":"paragraph","text":"张明霞同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238"},{"id":"c094705019","type":"paragraph","text":"来信早收到，退复为款！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238"},{"id":"017a9aa746","type":"paragraph","text":"《蝶恋花》一词可以在你们的刊物上发表。《游仙》改《赠李淑一》。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238"},{"id":"7c4f408b09","type":"paragraph","text":"祝你们好！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238"},{"id":"ee0a8672f9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238"},{"id":"11c3b5a4d6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年十一月廿五日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238"}],"page":{"id":"967a6ebdb3","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e987fbb238","start":358,"end":358}}}},"__N_SSG":true}